### Files to create
- internal/service/videoqueue.go        — VideoQueue service
- internal/service/videoqueue_test.go
- internal/service/filetransfer.go      — FileTransferService
- internal/service/filetransfer_test.go
- internal/service/timelapse.go         — TimelapseService
- internal/service/timelapse_test.go
